Backpacker's Budget
Zoe is planning a trackpacking trip and aims to manage her expenses wisely by spending the same amount each day. At the end of the trip, Zoe would like to know her remaining budget. 
Can you assist Zoe in calculating the remaining budget? She will provide you with the following details:
The number of days on the trip.
The cost of expenses per day.
Zoe's initial budget

Input format:
The first line is the integer that represents the number of days on trip.
The second line is the decimal value that represents the cost of expenses per day.
The third line is the decimal value that represents the initial budget.

Output format:
The output is the decimal value that represents the remaining budget.

Note:
The remaining budget can also be negative.
The code for handling inputs is already been given, your task is to fill in the required code

